Requirements:
Java
Grails
MySQL Server 

Optional Tools:
MySQL Workbench
SpringSource Tool Suite



This project uses Grails 1.3.1.

Required Grail Plugins:

asynchronous-mail-0.1.3-SNAPSHOT
authentication-2.0.1
mail-0.9
quartz-0.4.2
webflow-1.3.5

See DataSource.groovy for database settings. 


This project also makes use of JQuery extensively. 

INSTALLATION
1) Install JDK 1.5+, add JAVA_HOME environment variable, 
add bin to PATH environment variable
2) Install Grails 1.3.x,  set GRAILS_HOME environment variable, 
add bin to PATH environment variable
3) Open console and cd to itda-web project directory
4) Run grails upgrade if required (not required for grails 1.3.1)
5) Run grails compile (if grails does not automatically installed the required plugin, install each plugin by running "grails install-plugin <plugin-name>"



run-app
* remove sessionFactory from Bootstrap
* update Datasource port username
